Class SpaceOutPost

  • java.lang.Object
    • SpaceOutPost
  • public class SpaceOutPost
extends java.lang.Object
    The SpaceOutPost object is used to handle all the medical supplies and foods. Instances of all of the foods and medical supplies are created and put into array lists when the SpaceOutPost object is created. This also holds the current money the user has.
